quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  49,14,"Nnan uâôaben n ucluê: \"numen\". Ini: \"ur tuminem\". Maca init ed: \"nunez\"; ur ikcim ara liman ar wulawen nnwen. Ma tôuvam Öebbi akked Umazan iS, ur awen Isôuêu acemma seg igiten nnwen. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  49,15,"Lmumnin d wid kan iumnen s Öebbi akked Umazan iS, d$a, ur pcukun. Pna$en s wayla nnsen akked yiman nnsen, deg ubrid n Öebbi. D widak ay d imawlan n tidep"
  49,16,"Ini: \"day ad aS temlem i Öebbi, ddin nnwen\"? Öebbi Iéôa i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Issen yal cci"
  49,17,"Rran ak annuz nnsen, d tajmilt. Ini: \"ur iyi telli tejmilt deg annuz nnwen. Xaîi, d Öebbi ikwen I$aten mi kwen Inha ar liman, ma d imawlan n tidep ay tellam"
  49,18,"Ih, Öebbi Issen tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan. Öebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"
  50,1,"S Leqwôan, mucaâ"
  50,2,"Xaîi! Wehmen mi ten id iusa uneddaô, segsen. Nnan ijehliyen: \"ayagi d lwehma"
  50,3,"Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, ayagi d tu$alin si mbâid"
  50,4,"Ni$ Neéôa acêal, segsen, i issenqes wakal. £uône£ Tazmamt iêerrzen"
  50,5,"Xaîi! Nekôen tidep, mi ten id tusa, d$a terwi lêala nnsen"
  50,6,"Day ur muqlen ara igenni, sennig sen, amek i t Nebna? Ncebbeê it, ur isâi i$isan"
  50,7,"Tamurt, Nvelq ip, Nerra degs idurar, Nessem$i d degs tayuga n yal ûûenf amxallef"
  50,8,i tmu$li akked usmekti n yal amdan isteôoiâen
  50,9,Nesse$li d seg igenni aman iôqan. Nessem$i d yissen leonanat akked uâqqa n tmegra
  50,10,"akked tezdayin ti$wezfanin, s ijeooigen mbabben"
  50,11,d ôôeéq i imdanen. Nessider d yissen tamurt immuten. Akka tanekra
  50,12,"Inkeô, uqbel nnsen, ugdud n Nuê, At Rrass, Tamud"
  50,13,"Âad, Ferâun, atmaten n Luî"
  50,14,"At Laika, akked ugdud n Tubbaâ. Nekôen akw imazanen. Iûaô ussigwed iW"
  50,15,Day £ issefcel uxlaq amezwaru? Wanag nitni di ccekk $ef uxlaq amaynut
  50,16,"Ni$ Nxelq ed amdan. Neéôa s wacu i t t$ewwu, teôwiêt is. Neqôeb $uôes, sennig iéuôan n temgaôt is"
  50,17,"Mara îîfen wid ippaîîafen; qqimen, wa $eô yeffus, wa $eô zelmev"
  50,18,"ur d iqqaô awal, siwa ma illa $uôes, uâssas imêelles"
  50,19,"Iusa d ddux n tmeppant, ibbwi d tidep: \"atan wayen iseg la treggwlev"
  50,20,Aûuvu di lbuq. D wagi ay d ass n ussigwed
  50,21,"Yal iman a d ias s unehhaô, akked unagi"
  50,22,"Ni$ telliv testehzav $ef waya. Nekkes ak taduli k. Iéôi k, assa, d uzzal"
  50,23,"Ad yini umsaâef is: \"ata $uôi wayen id ippuheggan"
  50,24,"Veggôet, ar Loahennama, yal ajehli amâaûi"
  50,25,"i iugwin lxiô, amjuô, imcebbwel"
  50,26,"i irran ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven. Ihi, veggôet ep s aâaqeb uqsiê"